Rising Adventure is a trekking company in Kathmandu, Nepal. We offer trekking, tour, and peak climbing not in Nepal only, but in Tibet and Bhutan. 
Our team really helps you to make your dreams come to true in the Himalayas of Nepal.
We also customize city sightseeing, bungee jumping, paragliding, rafting, kayaking, and other possible activities in Nepal.
You can contact us (https://www.risingadventure.com/contact-us) at any time. We are always there for fulfilling your requirements.
We also provide the essential information that you ask at free of cost.
